{"tid":1780694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭若驊發聲明再澄清「被迫留任」等完全無中生有","createTime":"2019-12-12T14:47:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T15:44:12.000Z","uid":13663,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"08de34821d8bb82fc97ef2d729ad714584138f9b","tid":1780694,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T14:47:31.000Z","msg":"鄭若驊發聲明再澄清「被迫留任」等完全無中生有<br />\n2019-12-12 HKT 22:29<br />\n<br />\n律政司司長鄭若驊晚上發聲明說，為免有人繼續發表失實言論，她再次澄清，所謂「被迫留任」等揣測完全是無中生有，早前針對有報道稱她曾經提出請辭，已作出否認並強調報道全無事實根據，重申不會請辭。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊表示，她答允這個任命時，已知道工作具挑戰性，現時面對艱難環境便提出請辭是不負責任。<br />\n<br />\n她在本月3日由北京返抵香港，在機場會見新聞界時已交代了她受傷後，由中國駐英國大使館安排回國到北京，前往醫院作進一步檢查和治療，當日出院後隨即返回香港。"},{"pid":"af8bf2c39a2dcf6fd577379d598f6ec12685379b","tid":1780694,"uid":80972,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T14:48:14.000Z","msg":"此地無銀"},{"pid":"31cfb99239da3be4aee8ff67c02a19b727d46a3a","tid":1780694,"uid":13663,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T14:49:36.000Z","msg":"To 大波驊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/waxH7cL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwaxH7cL.png&h=abda5aba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4850a2e65b3abf78c95bede1eb32138f420a14d1","tid":1780694,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T14:51:02.000Z","msg":"有樣嘢叫人怕出名豬怕肥<br />\n你完全收嗲可以令人隨時淡化"},{"pid":"a429f158d2c2221d6c5238aa5ca0695344dadead","tid":1780694,"uid":58527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T14:54:41.000Z","msg":"無中生有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />失實言論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無事實根據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲用字一睇就知又係中共寫既稿"},{"pid":"01048bc12f29bb0b563bea05d13476e1ea914342","tid":1780694,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T14:59:11.000Z","msg":"好撚慘呀，被迫出聲明<img src=\"/assets/faces